      <title>高盛称，随着 DeepSeek 的出现，对冲基金暂停了对美国人工智能的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-were-pausing-us-ai-bets-deepseek-emerged-says-goldman-2025-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛在一份报告称，随着中国新的人工智能模式逐渐兴起并挑战美国在该领域的主导地位，对冲基金也在观望美国培育的本土人工智能热潮是否会持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-were-pausing-us-ai-bets-deepseek-emerged-says-goldman-2025-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:57:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
